 $H^{*}$,\nimplying no influence of the QDW on the SC phase switching. We do not detect\nthe QDW transition within the SC2 state. A basic analysis with the\nGinzburg-Landau theory suggests that we have a weak competing interaction\nbetween the two order parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 22 Jan 2023 16:35:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Feb 2023 16:09:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-03"}
