lations conducted on starlink constellation with\nthousands of satellites corroborate the effectiveness of the proposed\nalgorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2023 11:32:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-24"}
